subSubSection.paragraph:
Male genitalia
: Left paramere (
Fig. 80
) with basal stem slender, main body broadened, then narrowing to a sharp hook apically. Right paramere (
Fig. 81
) with a slender stem, elongate main body, and bluntly rounded apex.
